Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.30,0:02:44.18,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.77,0:02:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the pirates who are \Nafter the One Piece...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.14,0:02:55.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...head for the New World, \Nthe second half of the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.15,0:03:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body turned \Nto rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.32,0:03:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and his friends venture into that sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.99,0:03:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.71,0:03:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On their way to the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.42,0:03:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy and his crew reached the Fish-Man \NIsland located 10,000 meters below sea level,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.92,0:03:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,where the New Fish-Man Pirates who are \Nlooking to destroy the Ryugu Kingdom...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.30,0:03:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...assisted by Vander Decken, who is after\NShirahoshi, are engaging in secret maneuvers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.60,0:03:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Straw Hats find themselves \Ncaught up in the turmoil.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.11,0:03:45.16,B1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2000,2000)}"Back to the Present!\NHordy Makes a Move!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.82,0:04:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jimbei!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.45,0:04:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! Who shot our queen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.91,0:04:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look for the shooter!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.75,0:04:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave no stone unturned!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.46,0:04:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother Tai! Queen Otohime! I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.51,0:04:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do with this anger?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.02,0:04:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit! Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.90,0:05:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There he is! We found the shooter!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.90,0:05:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Get to the rooftop now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.16,0:05:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he the shooter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.28,0:05:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He had a gun in his hand. There is no doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.41,0:05:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.37,0:05:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.75,0:05:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jimbei-san! We just killed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.25,0:05:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.92,0:05:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.88,0:05:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.80,0:05:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...human!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.39,0:05:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hide the body!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.52,0:05:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Boss Jimbei!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.69,0:05:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will ruin the Queen's efforts!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.99,0:05:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She won't be able to rest in peace like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.91,0:05:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it is what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.58,0:06:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, because he was a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.75,0:06:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter if he was a pirate or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.26,0:06:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Hordy! Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.35,0:06:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.31,0:06:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a human...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.77,0:06:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...who killed our queen!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.03,0:06:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Queen Otohime was killed by a human!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.37,0:06:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't deserve it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.63,0:06:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A human...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.46,0:06:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...killed the Queen who wanted \Nnothing but peaceful coexistence
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.76,0:06:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and broke our hearts just when we were\N inspired by her words and about to...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.64,0:06:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...extend our friendship!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.14,0:07:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He took our beloved one's life!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.40,0:07:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even by taking your life,\N Otohime-sama can never come back, human!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.53,0:07:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there no justice in this world?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.08,0:07:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so sad! Unbelievably sad!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.05,0:07:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is the King still in the Hard Shell Tower?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.64,0:07:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minister of the Left!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.81,0:07:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you hear that? He's lost all control.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.28,0:07:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,King-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.82,0:07:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lock the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.57,0:07:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't open it while I have \Nthis urge to kill someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.35,0:08:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,King-sama, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.44,0:08:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minister of the Left.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.90,0:08:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The shooter had a gun in his hand so \None of our soldiers shot him dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.90,0:08:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.82,0:08:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would have killed him \Neven if he were unarmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.50,0:08:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Otohime would not allow that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.34,0:08:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know when this \Ncycle of revenge started.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.67,0:08:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if I kill somebody, I would \Nonly perpetuate that cycle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.59,0:09:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Witnessing my actions would\N make children's eyes cold
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.26,0:09:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and they would harbor \Nhatred and become bitter,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.06,0:09:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the cycle of revenge spiraling on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.40,0:09:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could relate to what Otohime was saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.78,0:09:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...as long as it was somebody else's problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.86,0:09:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.70,0:09:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...why shouldn't I kill the man\N who shot my wife to death?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.21,0:09:29.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't understand that-jamon...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.50,0:09:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a soldier, I have taken many \Nlives in reprisal for my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.93,0:09:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I killed many humans who besieged us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.60,0:09:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is why I thought I have no place \Nhelping Otohime in what she was doing
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.06,0:09:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I just stood by and watched.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.52,0:09:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why should an innocent one like \Nher die and a man like me still live?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.45,0:10:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take over her quest \Nbecause my hands are sullied
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.45,0:10:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by what I have done in the past-jamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.45,0:10:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But we all change and we all \Nare full of contradictions.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.88,0:10:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We Fish-Men, and humans too. And there are \Nthings that only soldiers can protect.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.68,0:10:24.68,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}A FEW DAYS LATER
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.27,0:10:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,King-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.98,0:10:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.98,0:10:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my own wife's funeral \N- I have to attend it-jamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.37,0:10:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father-sama! Father-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.79,0:10:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shirahoshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.38,0:10:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.46,0:10:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My sons.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.97,0:11:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.01,0:11:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry to make you feel so left alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.65,0:11:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Father-sama, look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.65,0:11:13.94,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,TO SHIRAHOSHI
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.65,0:11:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.11,0:11:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These letters keep flying in wherever I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.95,0:11:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are already 5 of them, Father-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.12,0:11:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.66,0:11:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...a love letter! \NBut Shirahoshi is only 6 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.66,0:11:33.00,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,I'M IN LUV WITH YOU. I SUSPECT.\N MARRY ME. VANDER DECKEN
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.25,0:11:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is Vander Decken?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.00,0:11:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the name of a pirate family.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.46,0:11:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My children won't attend the funeral!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.97,0:11:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.09,0:11:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There could be an accomplice\N still lurking around.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.18,0:11:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And catch this pirate named Decken now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.22,0:11:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.60,0:12:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.93,0:12:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at the monitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.77,0:12:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Prince Fukaboshi!\N--Prince-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.19,0:12:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukaboshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.24,0:12:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Citizens of the Fish-Man Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.83,0:12:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is something I \Nwant to tell you all today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.79,0:13:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So please give me your attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.30,0:13:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In her last moment, my mother said happily,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.18,0:13:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"We are almost there at that\N place under the real sun."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.85,0:13:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have decided to take over
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.85,0:13:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,our mother's dream and dedicate\N our lives to seeing it through.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.02,0:13:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Princes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.94,0:13:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You probably are not going to be \Nready for the World Summit in 2 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.24,0:13:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there will be another one in \N6 years and another in 10 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.25,0:13:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure this tragedy made you\N change your view of humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.05,0:13:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I will get rid of all the \Nsignatures that were left unburned.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.01,0:13:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's start from the beginning!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.76,0:14:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And when your emotional\N wounds heal someday,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.48,0:14:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,let's dream about the sun together again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.35,0:14:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And for the decade that followed, \Nnot just Fukaboshi, Ryuboshi and Manboshi
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.52,0:14:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but also the King and the Princess spoke\N to the nation through the monitor
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.78,0:14:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,all while signatures kept mounting up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.87,0:14:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that was how we have been fighting against\N discrimination for the last 16 years
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.37,0:15:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the beginning of the Fish-Man Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.09,0:15:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arlong, who did horrible \Nthings to your hometown,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.05,0:15:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was like a brother to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.47,0:15:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he engaged in violence, we were willing to \Ngo anywhere in order to stop him ourselves
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.69,0:15:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but he always paid off the \NNavy soldiers around him...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.98,0:15:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to keep his actions secret from the Navy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.99,0:15:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a result, I made you \Nand many others suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.67,0:15:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel responsible!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.01,0:15:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.09,0:15:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why don't you cut your own belly?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.85,0:15:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.60,0:15:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pay her with your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.85,0:16:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still won't forgive you but it \Ncould relieve Nami-san of her pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.19,0:16:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, Sanji-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.86,0:16:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Nami-san, what they \Nhave done to you was...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.69,0:16:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a different story!\N This man didn't mean to hurt us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.57,0:16:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.62,0:16:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will take any punishment!\N If it makes you happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.37,0:16:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.38,0:16:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop. The only one I hate is Arlong.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.80,0:16:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I'm glad that you are not the \Nmastermind of the Arlong Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.60,0:16:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you're Luffy's friend, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.60,0:16:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that I've gone through \Nhell because of the Arlong Pirates
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.02,0:16:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I met my friends in \Nthat horrible turmoil.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.74,0:16:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One thing led to another\N and I am who I am today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.20,0:17:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna hate you \Nbecause you're a Fish-Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.83,0:17:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So don't pity me because of my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.75,0:17:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not so bad because I'm \Nenjoying it in the present!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.51,0:17:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it doesn't matter who did this...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.68,0:17:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get angry on my behalf.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.90,0:17:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell the people \Non the island anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.11,0:17:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Neither the tragedy we endured \Nnor of our anger towards humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.11,0:17:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, Jimbei.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.78,0:17:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two grew up together and\N he's like a brother to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.49,0:17:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder you couldn't just kill \Nhim even though you were justified.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.84,0:17:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't deserve such words of kindness!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.64,0:18:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.27,0:18:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.32,0:18:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss Jimbei-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.74,0:18:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! I know how hard it is to be a big brother!\N You're the man, Jimbei!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.25,0:18:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like Tiger and Otoshime \Nand everybody very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.54,0:18:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, Franky!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.92,0:18:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He must've been feeling so much pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.47,0:18:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.39,0:18:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.40,0:18:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.23,0:18:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.95,0:19:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a good nap.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.37,0:19:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe it! I thought it was \Nunusual for you to listen so quietly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.29,0:19:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Jimbei, are you crying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.67,0:19:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying? I am not crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.76,0:19:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.55,0:19:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out! I said I am not crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.51,0:19:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmmm... Oh, well!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.72,0:19:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Jimbei, what did happen to the \Nthief that Coward's mother caught?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.60,0:19:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must've been sleeping most of \Nthe time! That was the very beginning!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.06,0:19:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Was it?\N--It was!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.53,0:19:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, so your name is Shirahoshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.20,0:19:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nami-chin, she's the Princess!\N You can't say "Hey"...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.33,0:19:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Oh, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.20,0:19:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was crying remembering my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.71,0:19:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was quite a woman, wasn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.67,0:19:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.13,0:20:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you are Nami-chin-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.13,0:20:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Mermaid Princess-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.30,0:20:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-chin is like her nickname.\N Her real name has no "chin."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.51,0:20:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels like I have known you since I was a \Nkid although we just met for the first time...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.60,0:20:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel comfortable with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.65,0:20:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah? Maybe that's because we've\N been through similar things.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.16,0:20:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.53,0:20:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I took too much time. I need to know \Nwho is still at the Ryugu Palace now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.17,0:20:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hordy and his crew invaded the palace \Nand captured the King and his soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.38,0:20:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you don't know what \Nhappened to four of your crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.63,0:20:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all the information we have so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.14,0:20:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jimbei-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.97,0:20:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If things are going as Hordy planned,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.68,0:20:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the whole country might be \Nin a terrible state by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.77,0:21:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what his plan is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.40,0:21:05.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suspected he was up to something\N in the Fish-Man District
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.11,0:21:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,after retiring from the army,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.70,0:21:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but he never revealed it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.87,0:21:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.83,0:21:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hordy hates humans more\N than Arlong-san did.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.46,0:21:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has been living on the resentment and \Nanger of the Fish-Men, and nothing else.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.68,0:21:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And there is something about him \Nclearly different from Arlong-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.35,0:21:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arlong-san would look down on humans \Nbut he would never hurt other Fish-Men.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.36,0:21:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Hordy will attack those Fish-Men\N who are sympathetic to humans...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.45,0:21:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...without mercy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.20,0:21:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This year is the World Summit which\N takes place every four years.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.46,0:21:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since they gathered enough signatures,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.37,0:22:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,King Neptune will express his \Nintention to the world finally,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.75,0:22:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to relocate the Fish-Man Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.68,0:22:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me he is planning to block it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.60,0:22:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, he wants more than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.90,0:22:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.69,0:22:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a big Transponder Snail!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.16,0:22:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a Video Transponder Snail!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.53,0:22:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it here?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.62,0:22:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! It's activated!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.46,0:22:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's projecting something on the bubble!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.63,0:22:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.64,0:22:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.89,0:22:55.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san, do you know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.77,0:22:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hordy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.02,0:23:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! That's him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.40,0:23:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hatchin!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.73,0:23:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, everybody on the Fish-Man Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.57,0:23:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.36,0:23:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the captain of the New Fish-Man \NPirates from the Fish-Man District,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.74,0:23:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hordy Jones!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.00,0:23:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hordy broadcasts his ambition \Nacross all of Fish-Man Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.29,0:23:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His shocking intention is \Nto destroy the Ryugu Kingdom
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.80,0:23:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and establish himself as the new king.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.76,0:23:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The citizens of Fish-Man Island \Nhad been deeply unsettled already,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.26,0:23:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but Hordy's announcement has \Nfurther filled them with dread!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.10,0:23:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.31,0:23:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Kingdom in Shock! \NAn Order to Execute Neptune Issued!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.77,0:23:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
